message.body: Going to try a different gym that's close to my office. There isn't one by my new apartment. I hope I'll like it
So when does your non profit start today?
Wait, did you move already?!
And again, I have yet to sleep when it is dark out. This is not a good start to the week...
Not yet. I figured I might as well have a membership close to work if not the apartment. Previous one ended last week too
Oh no =/ I don't suppose you have any methods of getting to sleep easily?
I tried zquil before. It seemed to work the first time but didn't the second time so I have up on it.
*gave
What about a good romp in the sac? Lolol
Um I don't think that's an option at the moment.
Sorry. Bad joke. Well maybe you can struggle through the day and not nap until sun down. Maybe that will reset the sleep cycle
Maybe I'll just continue living a backwards, dysfunctional life.
You can get it worked out eventually. I'm lacking sleep myself. I'm so crazy tired at my desk right now. I'm scared of nodding off in the middle of the day
Down that caffeine!!!
Haha unfortunately caffeine only makes me groggy
Take a nap underneath your desk.
I think about doing that often but my desk has my back facing away from the wall. So it would be pretty obvious if I were napping
Good suggestion though
Hahah I try. I definitely have some narcoleptic tendencies that is pretty strong at times. I would probably find a small space and try to fit in it to take a nap hahah.
I think about doing that constantly but always fear getting found
The fear might be fun.
But understandable.
That's a new brand of hide and go seek. Not only are you hiding but you're napping
It's sucks that you're sleepy and don't have the option to do so. Yet, I have the option, but can't sleep.
Life.
If we became one entity we would sleep forever lolol
That's the dream hahah.
But then again, nothing would get done and I won't get pancakes.
I'll make some. I'm not bad with making those.
Not fair, my chocolate chop pancakes usually bonds out heavier than I want them to.
You mean the batter or the actual cakes?
I think they're kind of intertwined.
Maybe tweak the recipe or try a deterrent one?
What's a deterrent one?
Different. Sorry I'm running around and not paying attention to my text input
Ohh yea, probably not a good idea to text you at work. My b. Have fun running around!
It's alright. I answer at my own discretion. Thanks :)
Staying alive for the little darlings I hope?
Nope. My sister hasn't left yet and I've since fell asleep around 1...until a few minutes ago...
Did my first gym session at work. Not bad. I take it you're not too fond of sleeping during the day
It's more so that I like to fall asleep while it's still dark out.
Guess you found your new gun?
*gym
Yeah. They have modern equipment and it's pretty clean on top of being cheap. Only 20/month I think.
Eyes of God - Prohodna cave in Bulgaria http://imgur.com/JgcRI9q So cool!
That is so cool looking!
So I just got up. This is terrible.
Good morning lol. I fought the urge to nap miraculously
Feeling drowsy our anything?
Hahah good morning. Then you have more willpower than me!
A bit. But it'll go away. It has to because I am not laying back down.
I have the urge to go to CVS actually hahah.
What's Phuong in need of from the almighty convenience drug monster?
I want to get Vitamins.
Well excuse me, Phuong wants to get Vitamins.
Lol I would've thought you got enough from all the eating you do
Always room for some extra nutrition.
I suppose. Do you feel you're lacking? Seemingly energetic enough
Well it's mostly preventative.
Ah. That's good. I used to eat the gummy vitamins. Mostly because they tasted good.
I'm still eating the gummy vitamins hahah.
No shame. I like em too heh
So I just found out from my mom that my sister is leaving at 4 a.m. This is going to be such a short day.
What will you do till then?
I'm sure you've already heard of this, but what color is this?ï¿¼
I see blue and gold
Well the debate has been between white and gold or blue and black.
http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/02/28/science/white-or-blue-dress.html?_r=0
Doing a little hookah tonight. What color do you see?
I saw both options at some point.
Cool, are you going out to a bar?
Isn't it the contrast that changes it?
Nah. We have it at the house
I guess, and the lighting.
Oh you and your roommate?
How is he taking the news that you're leaving?
Indeed. He suggested actually. After a year of trying to explain to him how we're different people he finally heard me and said I think you might prefer living on your own
How cordial.
I kinda need to get out of this neighborhood. The parking is terrible, no one really stops at stop signs, my car has been broken into and vandalized, and house was robbed when we went on vacation
Orange Glow at Teton Range, Wyoming. Taken by Robert Buman [1280 x
854] http://i.imgur.com/Xqavqo2.jpg Nature has
Wow, that is breath taking!
Are you a D.C. comics fan by chance?
I like the movies.
The Fortress of Solitude http://i.imgur.com/M84J9HO.jpg In honor of the superman versus Batman coming up
Hahahah! Not nice Batman.
Bruce and Tony are my favorites from their respective universes
Good choices.
Do you use flavored smoke?
Yeah we have blueberry. It's our best one
Yum.
Did you end up going to cvs?
It might be an early a.m. run.
Wanna get me some things while you're there?
Hahah what do you want?
I was kidding lol. I was curious how nice you were. =P
I probably would have messed with you and bought you the wrong items anyways ha ha ha.
Heh. Seems like we're on parallel mindsets
You have plans on Saturday or would the sister still be gone?
She doesn't come back until Monday.
Aww. I was gonna ask if you would join myself and a different group of friends for a little bar hopping
It's ok. I'll organize something nice at my new apartment and there will be Uyen with her going away party. At least I'm sure she'll have one
Oh yea, do you know when she's doing that?
Don't have the date. I'm sure she'll let us know
I really hope it's not this weekend.
I'll take over for you with the darlings
But then you wouldn't be able to go.
We would split the time of course
I hope it isn't this weekend either lol
I thought so hahah.
Would you really though? Do you actually trust me? =P
I think it would be overwhelming, and I wouldn't do that to you.
I think I would be alright. My two siblings came out ok lolol. Offer will stay on the table.
Did you sleep tonight?
Nope. I stayed up so my sister could sleep.
Such a nice sister you are
Plus, I think I'm having heartburn so it's not likely I'll be going to bed soon.
Stressing over sleep?
No, I tend to get it when I eat a heavy meal after a prolonged period.
It's not an uncommon experience for me so no biggie.
Still haven't gone to CVS though.
Hahah.
Even so. It should be avoided if possible. I don't think they open until 8?
There are some 24-hour ones.
Oh yeah. Forgot about that. That was the blessing of living in a college town. So many stores stay open late or 24
Oh the good old college days, when going to WAWA at 2 a.m. was not only acceptable, but expected!
Heh. For me it was r u hungry, canyon pizza (big ass pizza slices for a buck), the downtown diner, or wings over happy valley (awesome boneless wings drenched in sauce with waffle fries)
Wawa doesn't exist in western PA
Oh sucks for you. You were at the main campus right?
For the second half of my college career
Where was the first half spent?
Campus that is currently known as Brandywine. Formerly Delaware county campus. They changed it to not be confused with DCCC
Did you ever get stickies?
Yes. Unfortunately, no drunken state could ever convince me they were good. Almost always dry and not tasty.
What?! I want to try one!!!0
That's kind of disappointing to hear. But I would still try it.
Lol I'll bring you along if I ever return to the campus
Road trip!!!
Okay, exactly what is it anyways?
I'd rather introduce you to the creamery. The ice cream is more well known
Cinnamon sticks
A la mode is available too
(Add scoop of ice cream)
Sounds pretty darn tootin' good!
I don't have anyone to visit tough lol.
Can always order it offline I think.
Probably. Getting cinnabons would be more rewarding though lol
Oh yes, then there is that option.
So my sister's first flight connection got cancelled.
Well, shit
I drove them to the airport at 4, almost 5 a.m. and she was worried that they were going to be late because the flight leaves at 6. Then I got a text saying it was cancelled.
That is very unfortunate. Where were they headed?
DR
